機突然倒地，警員試圖按他在地上。司機隨後站起，警員嘗試再將其按下，其間有警員揮拳打向司機頭部，雙方倒向車CAM所在的車輛。司機最終被多名警員按在地上制服，暫未知有否受傷或是否被捕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"黑警=香港最大黑社會<br />\n共匪=中國最大黑社會"},{"pid":"84ce121079a4f996c29befaa5cf8667de08019e0","tid":1526262,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"警犬危害道路安全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2d7eae9cb8955708dde4cf1c6ad09c0b68beb5","tid":1526262,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa4cf2f8a436b0e7fb9eb6bde41f9cf9e1c1179","tid":1526262,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"你唔撚係教巴打塞入蝗軍把口呀嘛<br />\n咁撚癲咪痴線啦"},{"pid":"eb287e54d7d293a999ae0374986712928f4894a4","tid":1526262,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4e20347c47cf0e4bf4b8fe836114ce920eef35","tid":1526262,"uid":240104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:08:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe5fe9f4c5518c102869afc0dbe2314505332772","tid":1526262,"uid":95488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"正仆街 社會垃圾"},{"pid":"051aa01ca313a2b9b994a7eae4fa2cb6b4456d2c","tid":1526262,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95db4277b08b84ffa56219c26597f8f4a1d38452","tid":1526262,"uid":69719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0eb92591a959c73766ca784b2b5000c8b9e9ca8","tid":1526262,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:09:36.