":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=451490695578966&amp;id=333035294091174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D451490695578966%26id%3D333035294091174&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=6539313e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=451490695578966&amp;id=333035294091174</a><br />\n<br />\n警 察 撞 爛 貨 Van 側 鏡 司 機 理 論 原 告 變 被 告</blockquote>條路咁撚闊都有行埋面痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">剩得鋪狗力同良心賤賣，唔弱智都唔會當差啦！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd60b948a4fdf28a834d00f1d423e3310c625b8","tid":1526262,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"1df4101621ba0f82dd02d55498dc566db3646bc0","tid":1526262,"uid":274329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>901 機場攻略</strong></span><br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou/832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou%2F832&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=3f9880ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou/832</a><br />\n<br />\n宣布<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啟動應變計劃 Plan D</span></span></strong><br />\nA車同E車暫時仲入到機場<br />\n北大開始塞車，未入機場嘅手足可以考慮步入機場<br />\n注意補充水份，手足萬事小心<br />\n集合T1巴士總站<br />\n<br />\n機場手足一定要留意住現場旅客人數，旅客人數越多大家越安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=a3818cfb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58cecc942f62613999b5e71f0e4c4ebee38ad219","tid":1526262,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2000a880bc892e4ed6dc012f9a5edf598ef915b9","tid":1526262,"uid":187109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠"},{"pid":"85d0498dbca1e7a4b61c8ea85d0ec51ab91dbcaf","tid":1526262,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d790642b2beeda26e5ac45b7954919515f80e81f","tid":1526262,"uid":203794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"希望佢係藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0251700e67d042f71bb30d1cedbc72e26ac719fa","tid":1526262,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,